TextEng: Apologies won't save you now, mage! Die!
Perhaps you had better answer my questions before I finish what you started.
Text: 네가 시작한 일을 끝내기 전에 내 질문에 답하는 게 좋을 거야.

TextEng: I give you rash, bad guy! Die! Die!
Text: 나쁜 놈! 발진 줄게! 죽어! 죽어!

TextEng: I no got rash. You answer me questions now!
Text: 나 발진 안 났어. 이제 질문에 대답해!

TextEng: I have been sent here to take a magical gem from you.
Me come for magic gem.
I have no further questions.
Me have no more questions.
You are of no use to me. Die!
You useless! Die!
I have been hired to get the gem and I intend to get it. Hand it over now!
Text: 보석을 가져오라고 고용됐고 반드시 가져갈 거다. 당장 내놔!

TextEng: Elaith Serpent guy hire me so me gonna get the gem. Give it now!
Text: 엘레이스가 나 고용했어. 보석 가져갈 거야. 지금 줘!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That is not acceptable. Tell me what happened to the gem.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 그건 안 돼. 보석이 어떻게 됐는지 말해.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me say no. You tell me what happen to gem.
I do not care to listen to your excuses. Tell me where the gem is or suffer the consequences.
Text: 변명 듣고 싶지 않아. 보석이 어딨는지 말해. 안 그러면 대가를 치르게 될 거야.

TextEng: No excuses! You tell where gem or me hurt you good!
Text: 변명 싫어! 보석 어딨는지 말해. 안 그러면 아프게 해줄게!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> You say that YOU are unable to retrieve the gem but I believe that I have just proven myself to be stronger than you.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 네가 보석을 되찾을 수 없다고 했지만, 나는 방금 내가 너보다 강하다는 걸 증명한 것 같은데.

TextEng: Come on, you must have more than that. Hand it over!
Text: 이봐, 더 있을 거 아냐. 내놔!

TextEng: C'mon! You have more treasures! Gimme!
That is not enough! Give me more or I'll feed you a foot of sharpened steel!
Text: 그걸론 부족해! 더 내놔. 안 그러면 이 칼로 배를 갈라주지!

TextEng: Me want more or me stab you good!
Text: 더 줘! 안 그러면 찔러버릴 거야!

TextEng: Who are you?
I want your valuables. Anything and everything of value.
Text: 귀중품을 원해. 가치 있는 건 다.

TextEng: Who you be?
You give me gold and treasures.
Who are you, exactly?
That isn't how it works. You answer my questions or I kill you.
Text: 그런 식으론 안 돼. 내 질문에 답해. 안 그러면 죽인다.

TextEng: I dunno. Who you be?
Nuh-uh. You answer me or you die.
Text: 안 돼. 대답해. 안 그러면 죽어.

TextEng: Go on.
Enough of this. I have another question.
Story too long. Me have other question.
Text: 이야기 너무 길어. 다른 질문 있어.

TextEng: And the gem?
I care not. Let me ask you something else.
Me no care. Other question.
Where is this area and how do I get there?
Where be area and how me get there?
Give me the key to the door and I shall get the gem myself.
Text: 문 열쇠를 줘. 내가 직접 보석을 찾아오지.

TextEng: Gimme key and me get gem.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Is there anything in the area that could help me get through without becoming demon fodder?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그 구역에 악마 밥이 되지 않고 통과할 수 있게 도와줄 만한 게 있어?

TextEng: I will attempt to close the portal as I search for the gem.
Yeah, me try close portal for you.
If the reward is good.
What be reward?
I'm not interested. I just want the gem.
Me no care. Just want gem.
How about a little bit of the reward in advance?
Text: 보상을 조금 미리 받을 수 있을까?

TextEng: You give some reward now?
I haven't closed the portal yet.
Me no close portal yet.
What was I supposed to do again?
What you want me do again?
The portal has been closed.
Me close portal real good.
Goodbye.
Could you tell me the story about the portal again?
Me want to hear portal story again.
Text: 나 차원문 이야기 다시 듣고 싶어.

TextEng: You mentioned that you had lost the gem?
You say you lose gem?
We are both of the same race. Surely you could take that into consideration and offer a bit more.
Text: 우리 둘 다 같은 종족이잖아. 그걸 고려해서 좀 더 주면 안 될까?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I've just saved your home from a demon infestation. I want a bigger reward.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 네 집을 악마로부터 구해줬잖아. 더 큰 보상을 원해.

TextEng: Why don't you throw a little extra in so I won't have to hurt you again?
Text: 또 다치기 싫으면 좀 더 얹어주는 게 어때?

TextEng: Indeed. Farewell!
Me <race> kind. You <race> kind. Be nice to me.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me save you big demon trouble. You give more money?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 악마 문제 해결했어. 돈 더 줘?

TextEng: How 'bout you give more money and me not kill you real bad?
Text: 돈 더 주면 안 죽일게. 어때?

TextEng: Bye bye.
Sure. That would be handy.
Yuh, it move me so me no walk.
I'll find my own way out.
Me okay. Bye bye.
